<p>While things might seem perfect, her Twitter account was telling a different tale and Demi lamented that she has been marked after being stung by a jellyfish.</p>

<p>The thong song: Demi captioned the images with the words: 'todo perfecto' which means 'everything is perfect' in Spanish</p>

